Bluetooth connection attempt failed many times, please try the following suggestion:

 1. Check whether the bluetooth connector is powered on or within the effective distance of 10 metres.

 2. Open the system Settings program, switch to the Bluetooth item, unpair the bluetooth connector, go back to Diagnostic application to pair and connect the connector again.

 3. Reboot the unit, open Diagnostic application, and connect the connector again.

 4.Restart the host, enter into the diagnostic application system to reconnect.
